Abdomen
: yellow with medially divided black bands at distal half of each segment (
Fig. 30
), tergites with sparse short black setae, sternites yellow with sparse short white setae but sternites 1–2 with long soft dense white pubescence, sternite 8 black proximally, sternite 9 black. Males with black hair pencils between segments 6 and 7 (
Fig. 32
). 
